udio segmentation and merging**\n- MOCK-MISS: Yes — mocks would segment and merge without error\n- REAL-INFRA: Real speech-to-text API calls for each segment\n- MOCK-HIDE: Yes — mocking hides context loss across segments, merging failures, incoherence\n- LLM-DEP: Yes — multiple LLM calls (summarize each segment, then merge)\n- MULTI-STEP: Yes — real sequence: transcribe segments → summarize each → merge → final summary\n\nThis is **Workflow level** because the real failure is in orchestrating multiple LLM steps. Merging summaries coherently while maintaining speaker attributions requires the actual LLM calls in sequence, not mocks.\n\n---\n\n**Behavior 5: Full pipeline completes without manual intervention**\n- MOCK-MISS: Yes — mocks hide timeouts, rate-limiting, integration failures\n- REAL-INFRA: Yes — real file upload, real HTTP, real subprocess coordination\n- MOCK-HIDE: Yes — mocking hides real failure modes (API timeouts, format incompatibility, missing output)\n- LLM-DEP: Yes — multiple real LLM calls\n- MULTI-STEP: Yes — full pipeline: upload → transcribe → summarize → output delivery\n\nThis is **Workflow level** because it's the complete agent pipeline with real infrastructure at every boundary."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13631,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":13631},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f0d778da-ce60-470a-9146-9a698fd2639b","uuid":"bf6aaefd-c76e-42e7-8996-f877838f3bcf"}
